38enum EMaterialForceCastFlags
39{
40 MFCF_ForceCast = 1<<0, // Used by caller functions as a helper
41 MFCF_ExactMatch = 1<<2, // If flag set skips the cast on an exact match, else skips on a compatible match
42 MFCF_ReplicateValue = 1<<3 // Replicates a Float1 value when up-casting, else appends zero
43};

59/** What type of compiler is this? Used by material expressions that select input based on compile context */

61{
62 Standard, /** Standard HLSL translator */
63 Lightmass, /** Lightmass proxy compiler */
64 MaterialProxy, /** Flat material proxy compiler */
65};
